                                      <div class="article-paragraph"><h3>International Day of Clean Energy: 26 January 2026</h3><p><a href="https://www.un.org/en/observances/clean-energy-day/messages"><strong>Secretary-General's Message - 2026</strong></a><br><br><img src="/sites/default/d8files/inline-images/pexels-kelly-4320480.jpg" data-entity-uuid="cd702f3e-d181-4982-89d8-f4bfa24ec48d" data-entity-type="file" width="593" height="333"><br><br><strong>More resources:</strong> <a href="https://t.co/T1tRsINgJz" dir="ltr">buff.ly/GIRnGOr</a>&nbsp;<br><a href="https://x.com/i/status/2015689020559200759">https://x.com/i/status/2015689020559200759</a>&nbsp;<br><a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/r/174CK2fGMS/">https://www.facebook.com/share/r/174CK2fGMS/</a><br><a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DT-JYn9j--w/">Instagram</a></p><h3>&nbsp;Updated status of renewables in Asia and the Pacific</h3><h3><a href="https://unescap.org/sites/default/d8files/event-documents/Updated%20status%20of%20renewables%20in%20Asia%20and%20the%20Pacific.pdf"><img src="/sites/default/d8files/inline-images/Updated%20status%20of%20renewables%20in%20Asia%20and%20the%20Pacific_0.jpg" data-entity-uuid="d18d7480-2a80-4440-ac4f-95fab0bb47ca" data-entity-type="file" width="629" height="354"></a><br><br><img data-entity-uuid="982f5e1c-d8ea-4730-843e-eb28dc9204c2" data-entity-type="file" src="/sites/default/d8files/inline-images/Cover%20with%20QR%20code_V1.png" width="621" height="882"></h3><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Access on ESCAP Repository: <a href="https://hdl.handle.net/20.500.12870/9370">https://hdl.handle.net/20.500.12870/9370</a></p><p>&nbsp;</p></div>
                            
                                                    
                                        
                  </div>
          
                <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
          
                                        
                                      <div class="article-paragraph"><p><strong>Working towards SDG7 targets achievement, ESCAP’s energy&nbsp;work falls into three categories;</strong></p></div>
                            
                                        
                                        
          
                                                      <div class="card card-basic secondary ">
                                                    <div class="overlay-image ">
                                                            <div>
                                                          <img srcset="/sites/default/d8files/styles/max_325x325/public/2020-12/ED-text%20image.png?itok=QZGog06e 325w, /sites/default/d8files/styles/max_650x650/public/2020-12/ED-text%20image.png?itok=WMjfM8cs 650w, /sites/default/d8files/styles/max_1300x1300/public/2020-12/ED-text%20image.png?itok=yA35WdDa 1087w" sizes="(min-width: 1290px) 1290px, 100vw" width="325" height="160" class="js-lazyload-image js-lazyload-image" data-src="/sites/default/d8files/styles/max_325x325/public/2020-12/ED-text%20image.png?itok=QZGog06e" src="/sites/default/d8files/styles/thumbnail/public/2020-12/ED-text%20image.png?itok=wXKMKrbq" alt="" title="" loading="lazy" typeof="foaf:Image" />


                            </div>
                            </div>
                                            <div class="card-body">
    
                                
    
    
    
    
              </div>
             </div>
                                          
                                        
                                        
                                        
          
                                        
                                      <div class="article-paragraph"><p><em>Energy is the cornerstone of sustainable development. Demand for energy globally is rising and the Asia-Pacific region consumes more than half of global energy supply. Meeting rising energy demand and achieving universal access while ensuring energy sector development that is environmentally friendly, socially sound and economically feasible presents a significant challenge.</em></p><p><strong>OUR FOCUS AND SERVICES</strong></p><p>Our mission on energy is to ensure access to affordable, reliable, sustainable, and modern energy for all in Asia and the Pacific in line with Sustainable Development Goal 7 (SDG7) targets, and to enhance energy security and connectivity through regional cooperation We provide platform for dialogue and knowledge sharing and implements programmes to foster the transition to a sustainable energy system by advancing energy access, renewable energy, and energy efficiency.</p><p><strong>OUR WORK</strong></p><p><strong>Intergovernmental normative work</strong></p><ol><li><a href="https://www.unescap.org/intergovernmental-meetings/apef">Asia Pacific Energy Forum</a></li><li><a href="https://www.unescap.org/committee/committee-on-energy">Committee on Energy</a></li><li><a href="https://www.unescap.org/our-work/energy/ewg-on-energy-connectivity">Expert Working Group on Energy Connectivity</a></li><li><a href="https://www.unescap.org/our-work/energy/ewg-on-sdg7">Expert Working Group on SDG7</a><br>&nbsp;</li></ol><p>&nbsp;</p></div>
                            
                                        
                                        
          
                                        
                                      <div class="article-paragraph"><p><strong>Knowledge products and resources</strong></p><ol><li><a href="https://asiapacificenergy.org/"><u>Asia Pacific Energy Portal</u></a></li><li><a href="https://nexstepenergy.org/landing?_gl=1*1e4wnjd*_ga*MTA0ODc3NzA0MS4xNzAwMDM5MjA4*_ga_SB1ZX36Y86*MTczMzQ1NDQ3OC40MjcuMS4xNzMzNDU2MTM4LjE0LjAuMA..">National Expert SDG Tool for&nbsp;Energy Planning (NEXSTEP)</a></li><li><a href="https://www.unescap.org/our-work/energy/CETMToolkit">Critical Energy Transition Minerals Toolkit</a> &nbsp;New!</li><li>Flagship publications/resources</li></ol></div>
                            
                                        
                                        
          
                                        
                                      <div class="article-paragraph"><p><strong>Technical assistance &amp; capacity building&nbsp;</strong></p><ol><li><a href="https://www.unescap.org/projects/nexstep">SDG 7 road maps development</a> &nbsp;</li><li><a href="https://www.unescap.org/our-work/energy/capacity-building">Capacity Building on Energy</a></li><li>SPECA- Working Group on&nbsp;Energy, Water and&nbsp;Environment</li><li>Regional Economic&nbsp;Cooperation and Integration&nbsp;(RECI)- Energy</li><li><a href="https://www.unescap.org/our-work/energy/energy-sustainable-development/evidence-based-policies">Development Account Projects</a></li></ol></div>
                            
                                        
                                        
